{"tid":1162094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張建宗: 會認真探索在香港以外地方引入勞工","createTime":"2019-05-19T15:35:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T01:14:49.000Z","uid":54733,"like":2,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"61eae95afa9a81dcb4bfd9b18be05cf212a2417d","tid":1162094,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T15:35:54.000Z","msg":"政務司司長張建宗指，會認真探索在香港以外地方引入勞工。 <br />\n<br />\n張建宗於網誌撰文，指在人口高齡化和低生育率的影響下，本港未來人力供應將會萎縮，二零二七年整體人力預計會短缺近十七萬人，各級教育程度的人力基本上也會出現短缺，初中及以下程度會出現最大的人力短缺，推算二零二七年的短缺有七萬六千五百人。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n張建宗指婦女、少數族裔以及新來港人士等等，都是重要的人力資源，對補足本地勞動力一個都不能少，政府會繼續推動人才培訓及多項就業實習計劃等，亦會適度針對人手嚴重不足的行業，認真探索在香港以外地方引入人力。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/548845/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E5%BC%B5%E5%BB%BA%E5%AE%97%E6%8C%87%E6%9C%83%E8%AA%8D%E7%9C%9F%E6%8E%A2%E7%B4%A2%E5%BC%95%E5%85%A5%E5%A4%96%E5%8B%9E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F548845%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%25AE%2597%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%259C%259F%25E6%258E%25A2%25E7%25B4%25A2%25E5%25BC%2595%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%258B%259E&d=3iEKCEnQ8TgOeM43nfYZ113VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=57e02430\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F548845%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%25AE%2597%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%259C%259F%25E6%258E%25A2%25E7%25B4%25A2%25E5%25BC%2595%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%258B%259E&h=02abdc50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/548845/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E5%BC%B5%E5%BB%BA%E5%AE%97%E6%8C%87%E6%9C%83%E8%AA%8D%E7%9C%9F%E6%8E%A2%E7%B4%A2%E5%BC%95%E5%85%A5%E5%A4%96%E5%8B%9E</a>"},{"pid":"508ce9570f2b1711e32c52a1